general.name: ssppOut
general.short: migrated from old datamodel - needs update
general.description: This file consolidates the ssppOut results from the SSPP pipeline for all plates associated with a given data release. The format is similar to the individual ssppOut files, but some additional columns are added. For the SEGUE-2 targets associated with each star, see the associated ssppTargets file.
general.naming_convention: ssppOut-dr[0-9]+\.fits, where [0-9]+ is the data release number.

changelog.description: Describes changes to the datamodel product and/or file structure from one release to another
